{"tid":37762,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"越接近聖誕個人就越灰","createTime":"2016-12-13T13:49:59.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T14:14:56.000Z","uid":14371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0ad6c53d6da0acc8d6020090ab065965ea07617a","tid":37762,"uid":14371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T13:49:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac4ab1c38999ac2f098324f15a17da879f1a6e81","tid":37762,"uid":61765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T13:50:30.000Z","msg":"點解"},{"pid":"2a2e548d220687cf52d282ae273170928fc33434","tid":37762,"uid":14371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T13:51:40.000Z","msg":"天氣又忽冷忽熱搞到個人病病地<br />\n好撚頭痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重有一大堆報告未做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f272fd80df96a1b0318b82e6768e125f0d6c91","tid":37762,"uid":61765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T13:52:14.000Z","msg":"加油啦 早睡早起會有用"},{"pid":"33408a6f1b39d280fc651bf123705e308f163da9","tid":37762,"uid":14371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T13:52:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解</blockquote><br />\n你唔會咩<br />\n因為無女<br />\n聖誕節天氣又變凍緊想有個人陪下自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6eae2118a170c68becff95ce8748258131291fc","tid":37762,"uid":14371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T14:08:49.000Z","msg":"本身諗住聖誕同佢一齊過(一班朋友有男有女)<br />\n點知佢比人溝左 重要係交友apps識返黎<br />\n雖然我都知佢唔會鍾意我(性格太鳩又成日蝦佢)<br />\n我都知無可能永遠維持朋友狀態<br />\n遲早佢都會比人溝走<br />\n但估唔到咁快比人搶走 重要一個月仔交友apps <br />\n連同佢過一次聖誕節既機會都無<br />\n喊又喊唔出純粹個人好灰好sad<br />\n而且煩緊佢會唔會比人呃<br />\n連人中都唔多想打<br />\n突然間無左目標你要我聖誕點臨時臨急搵第二個目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n身邊連可以面對面傾依件事既朋友都無<br />\n個lihkg ac重要係朋友借比我一齊用<br />\n希望佢睇唔到依個post<br />\n我真係好懦弱"},{"pid":"d309ce0ea4aba1aefc7badf7ca7893ed7b48b5b4","tid":37762,"uid":14371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T14:11:37.000Z","msg":"第二次係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連想自己一個人靜下既地方都無<br />\n室友長期係房<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好啦我都係死返去繼續打報告<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08371f77150708ca014106f27ba47afc66639d85","tid":37762,"uid":14371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T14:13:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第二次係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連想自己一個人靜下既地方都無<br />\n室友長期係房<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好啦我都係死返去繼續打報告<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一次都好d<br />\n有個朋友陪我一齊失戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b75d8cdc3970cfc89bcffca693df74b30b40e4bd","tid":37762,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T14:14:56.000Z","msg":"一齊研究聖經"}]}